<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 7 (Xinhua) -- '97 China (Hong Kong)
Investment Symposium, the first major investment promotion event
after Hong Kong's return to China on July 1, opened here
today.
</P>
<P>
Entering its fourth year, the symposium has a record-breaking
total of 29 provinces, autonomous regions, municipalities and
cities from China's interior visiting Hong Kong to showcase some
900 investment projects, said An Min, assistant minister of
Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation.
</P>
<P>
