transfer and a central parts depot, opened two years after an
investment license was issued by the Vietnamese government.
</P>
<P>
A joint venture with Kuo (Asia) Pte. of Singapore and Vietnam's
Ministry of Industry, TMV is working with Vietnamese suppliers to
use local parts, starting with seats, wire harnesses and tools.
</P>
</TEXT>
