Liberation:
</P>
<P>
-- Sheikh Ahmed Yassin, the spiritual leader of the Palestinian
Hamas group, returned to Gaza on Monday in triumph, while two
Israeli agents who tried to assassinate a Hamas leader in Amman were
also returned by Jordan without revealing their true names or
identity.
</P>
<P>
