<HEADLINE> Chinese President Meets With American Business Group </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 7 (Xinhua) -- President Jiang Zemin, meeting
today with Goran Lindahl, executive president of the US's ABB
group, and with former U.S. Senator Bennet Johnston, said he
appreciates the group's fruitful co-operation with China in
manufacturing power equipment and developing China's power
industry.
</P>
