<HEADLINE> Canadian Ambassador to Mexico Resigns </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, October 6 (Xinhua) -- Canadian ambassador to Mexico
Marc Perron has resigned over his comments about corruption in
that country, local reports said today.
</P>
<P>
Perron tendered his resignation and will return to Canada,
Foreign Minister Lloyd Axworthy said today.
</P>
<P>
