<HEADLINE> (Urgent) Atlantis Lands on Earth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 6 (Xinhua) -- U.S. shuttle Atlantis, on the
mission to the Russian Mir in the space, landed safely shortly
before 6:00 EDT (2200 GMT) in Florida today. 
</P>
</TEXT>
